Reasoning: The paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically with compositing virtual objects into photographs in a camera-aware manner. This involves color transformation and inference, which are key topics in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and image processing, which could fall under cs.GR (Computer Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of machine learning and deep learning techniques suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
